---
---

<!-- Section 4: Why choose us (trust / value props) -->
<section class="section con-why">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="con-why__head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Why Menon Medispa</p>
      <h2 class="con-why__heading">Expert Care, Built Around You</h2>
      <p class="con-why__intro">
        A consultation here isn&rsquo;t a sales pitch. It&rsquo;s a thoughtful, medically-informed plan
        from a team that treats your skin like its own.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="con-why__grid">

      <div class="con-why__card">
        <span class="con-why__icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"></circle><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"></line></svg></span>
        <h3 class="con-why__card-title">Expert Assessment</h3>
        <p class="con-why__card-body">
          Licensed professionals analyze your skin type, concerns, and goals to build a treatment
          roadmap that&rsquo;s genuinely yours.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="con-why__card">
        <span class="con-why__icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="4" y1="21" x2="4" y2="14"></line><line x1="4" y1="10" x2="4" y2="3"></line><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="3"></line><line x1="20" y1="21" x2="20" y2="16"></line><line x1="20" y1="12" x2="20" y2="3"></line><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="7" y2="14"></line><line x1="9" y1="8" x2="15" y2="8"></line><line x1="17" y1="16" x2="23" y2="16"></line></svg></span>
        <h3 class="con-why__card-title">Customized Treatment Plans</h3>
        <p class="con-why__card-body">
          No two skins are alike. Your plan is tailored to your needs and desired outcomes, never a
          one-size-fits-all package.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="con-why__card">
        <span class="con-why__icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2"></rect><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"></rect><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"></line><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"></line><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"></line><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"></line><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"></line><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"></line><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"></line><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"></line></svg></span>
        <h3 class="con-why__card-title">Advanced Technology</h3>
        <p class="con-why__card-body">
          We pair medical-grade technology with evidence-based treatments to deliver exceptional,
          lasting results for every skin type.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .con-why .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .con-why__head {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  /* dark text, not gold: the brand gold is unreadable on this light section background */
  .con-why__head .eyebrow { margin: 0; color: var(--color-text); opacity: 0.65; }

  .con-why__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .con-why__intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .con-why__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .con-why__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: rgba(196, 164, 132, 0.07);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .con-why__icon {
    color: var(--color-cta);
    line-height: 0;
  }
  .con-why__icon svg {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    display: block;
  }

  .con-why__card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-subheading);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: var(--space-xs) 0 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .con-why__card-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .con-why__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
